oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: New Ivy Bluff Methodist Church
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Photograph of the new Ivy Bluff United Methodist Church, built in 1905. An interior and exterior photograph are included. The church burned to the ground from arson in October 2012 and was later rebuilt.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: Looking Back at Tennessee Photograph Collection, 1890-1981
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Methodist churches
